:0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"想問下焗爐分兩層焗麵包可唔可行?<br />\n如果唔係要分兩次焗? 驚佢發酵又變相耐左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc55636e2144e5d82d3e2964463e8b6787e7a622","tid":2308473,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51f7141297cb87534b365a0222ccab68f929834a","tid":2308473,"uid":110202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"想問下焗爐分兩層焗麵包可唔可行?<br />\n如果唔係要分兩次焗? 驚佢發酵又變相耐左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"好問題！<br />\n<br />\n我都困惑過<br />\n<br />\n如果焗爐夠大，應該係無問題既<br />\n但焗爐太細既，頂層太近發熱線就會燶！<br />\n<br />\n我上星期做outback包都係分兩層<br />\n因為我蒸焗爐<br />\n唔係上下發熱線<br />\n上層問題不大<br />\n下層明顯無漲得靚<br />\n但可以接受！<br />\n<br />\n如果真係分唔到兩層，<br />\n第一批先發酵，<br />\n後一批入一入雪櫃阻礙佢個發酵速度，<br />\n等第一批發酵好拎出黎，等佢回溫發酵會比較保險"},{"pid":"64a53a6d4af262e4600bebf0647448ddbcf0766f","tid":2308473,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"97f2f44db2d443336672c0c14b2da7c0d26a75ac","tid":2308473,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c02f15d1cf47d0b381d44c2a578e163c019d105","tid":2308473,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0a4c5c5845003e99cf9d295848cb1d59930c656f","tid":2308473,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"你快d嫁啦！嫁左就可以整喇！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"到時要買個大嘅氣炸鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji